NFCCreditCardTool - Android software
------------------------------------

* Introduction:
"Quick and dirty" proof-of-concept for Android
Open source tool developped and showed for Hackito Ergo Sum 2012 - "Hacking the NFC credit cards for fun and debit ;)" and Shakacon 2012.
Reads NFC credit card personal data (gender, first name, last name, PAN, expiration date, transaction history...) 

* Requirements:
Android NFC phone

* Known bugs and limitations:
- Supports only Visa "CB" credit cards (AID = A0 00 00 00 42 10 10)
- No support for currency and country in history (always shows â‚¬ and doesn't display country)
- Needs code cleaning

